      "title": "## Overview",
      "content": "This plan outlines the creation of a luxury online jewelry store for Laxmi Jewellers, featuring a comprehensive catalog of gold, diamond, platinum, and silver jewelry across various categories, occasions, and styles, with integrated e-commerce functionalities and trust-building elements."
