    {
      "id": "key-features",
      "title": "## Key features",
      "content": "- **View Product Listing**: Displays all jewelry items available for sale, organized by category, segmentation, and product type.\n- **Filter Products**: Allows users to filter jewelry by category (Gold, Diamond, Platinum, Silver), segmentation (Women, Men, Kids, Teens), product type (Rings, Earrings, etc.), occasion, metal type, and shopping segments (trending, customizable, budget, investment).\n- **View Product Details**: Shows detailed information for a single jewelry item, including descriptions, metal types, certifications, and pricing.\n- **View Trending Products**: Highlights popular and in-demand jewelry designs.\n- **View Customizable Jewelry**: Showcases jewelry options that can be personalized by the customer.\n- **View Budget Options**: Presents jewelry items within specific price ranges.\n- **View Investment Products**: Features items like gold coins suitable for investment.\n- **View Product Guides**: Provides educational content to help users understand jewelry types, metals, and certifications.\n- **View FAQ Listing**: Displays a list of frequently asked questions about products, services, and policies.\n- **View FAQ Item Details**: Shows the answer to a specific frequently asked question.\n- **Submit Customization Request**: Allows users to submit requests for custom jewelry designs.\n- **View Offers**: Displays current promotions, discounts, and special deals.\n- **Submit Newsletter Signup**: Allows users to subscribe to receive updates and offers via email.\n- **View Brand Story**: Presents information about the history, values, and mission of Laxmi Jewellers.\n- **View Testimonials**: Showcases customer reviews and feedback.\n- **View Educational Content**: Provides articles and information related to jewelry care, history, and trends.",
